Using this command you can make anyone moderator. It's one of the most unique and best command.

Command: ?makemod

Response: {delete} {require:<admin or higher rolename>} {dm:$1} $2+ {!setnick $1 ‚ôè$1.user.nick} {!role $1 +<Moderator rolename>} Hello $1, Congratulations now you are Official Moderator of {server}! and the reason of promoting you is $2+. {!announce <#(logging channel id)> $1 got promoted to mod role by {user} because of $2+.}

Use it like-
?makemod @user <reason of promoting him to mod>
